------------------

Port Notes:

----- version 1.0-3 -----
Rebuilt with builtin libgetaddrinfo to avoid extra dependencies.

----- version 1.0-2 -----
Rebuilt against shared libgetaddrinfo instead of including sources.

----- version 1.0-1 -----
Initial release for Cygwin for X11R7.2.


Cygwin port maintained by:
http://cygwinports.dotsrc.org/
